<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
        <link href="/assets/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <style type="text/css">
            body {
                background-image: url("/assets/vote.png");
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-position: 20px 50px;
                background-color: #d1d1d1;
                height: 100%;
                min-height: 7rem;
            }
            .container {
                background: white;
                padding: 1rem;
                border-radius: 10px;
                border: 1px solid #2a1c69;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }
            .header {
                padding-left: 5rem;
                padding-right: 5rem;
                padding-top: 1rem;
                padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }
            .footer {
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 0;
                width: 100%;
                height: 60px;
                line-height: 60px;
            }

        </style>

        {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body>
    <div class="header">
    <img src="/assets/logo-r2as.png" width="400px">
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <center>
            <span class="text-black">
                <a class="text" href="/">R2AS vote</a> : un service gratuit fourni par <a href="http://r2as.org/">R2AS</a> sans aucune garantie. Aucun cookie. Logiciel libre, <a href="https://github.com/cleming/r2as-vote">code source et informations</a>.
            </span>
        </center>
    </footer>
        {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
    </body>
</html>
